channel.title: I keep dying!
channel.description:
Hello! I have downloaded a DeltaScape source and I finally fixed the part where it doesn't create your account, causing lots of nulls to fill up the server. But now that I log in I see a lot "You have defeated M4 Carbine" (M4 Carbine is my new username in all of the servers).
Here is a picture!
[IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj23/FfsDied/Errors-1.jpg[/img]
Any ideas how to fix it?
Please don't say you don't deserve it or anything... I'm just not good with anti-leech, plus how the hell would I know how to fix that!
Also the prayer star seems easier but I can't see what's wrong with it! I overlooked the class31_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.java file but I couldn't see anything wrong!
Thanks in advance! Skullator(M4 Carbine)
